title: QUESTION TIME - The Hundred Sale and England's white-ball crisis
description: An update on The Hundred franchise sales and what it means for the domestic game, analysis of England's white-ball woes and an interesting admission from a man who many believe should be in England's one day squad, Liam Dawson.
